Reasoning: The paper discusses the development of a system that performs linguistic and semantic analysis to determine the causes of an accident report. This falls under the field of natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (CL), which is covered by the cs.CL sub-category. Additionally, the use of inference rules and the development of a system that can perform human-like reasoning suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper may also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves analyzing and extracting information from text. Finally, the mention of a "general framework" suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the field of cybernetics (cs.CY).
